---
import Container from "../shared/Container.astro";
import Paragraph from "../shared/Paragraph.astro";
---

<section  id="cta" >
  <Container>
    <div
      class="w-full relative  md:py-10 px-6 md:px-8 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-tr from-gray-100 to-gray-200 dark:from-gray-900"
    >
      <div class="absolute right-0 top-0 h-full w-full flex justify-end">
        <div class="w-28 h-28 overflow-hidden flex rounded-xl relative blur-2xl">
            <span
              class="absolute w-16 h-16 -top-1 -right-1 bg-green-500 rounded-md rotate-45"
            ></span>
            <span
              class="absolute w-16 h-16 -bottom-1 -right-1 bg-[#FCDC58] rounded-md rotate-45"
            ></span>
            <span
              class="absolute w-16 h-16 -bottom-1 -left-1 bg-primary rounded-md rotate-45"
            ></span>
          </div>
      </div>

      <div class="absolute left-0 bottom-0 h-full w-full flex items-end">
        <div class="w-28 h-28 overflow-hidden flex rounded-xl relative blur-2xl">
            <span
              class="absolute w-16 h-16 -top-1 -right-1 bg-green-500 rounded-md rotate-45"
            ></span>
            <span
              class="absolute w-16 h-16 -bottom-1 -right-1 bg-[#FCDC58] rounded-md rotate-45"
            ></span>
            <span
              class="absolute w-16 h-16 -bottom-1 -left-1 bg-primary rounded-md rotate-45"
            ></span>
          </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mx-auto text-center max-w-xl md:max-w-2xl relative">
        <h1
          class="text-3xl/tight sm:text-4xl/tight md:text-5xl/tight
          font-bold text-heading-1"
        >
          Comienza ya <br><span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-600 from-20% via-primary via-30% to-green-600">tu estrategia digital</span>
        </h1>
        <Paragraph className={"pt-10"}>
          Tener una web ya no es un aspecto que te diferencie de tu competencia. <br><b>Debes destacar en línea y llegar a tu audiencia potencial.</b> <br><br>¡Contáctanos ahora para dar el próximo paso!
                         
        </Paragraph>
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-md sm:max-w-xl pt-6">
          <form action="https://formsubmit.co/wwizard.lab@gmail.com" method="POST" id="contactForm" class="text-center">
            <label for="nombre" class="block text-gray-700 text-sm font-bold mb-4"></label>
            <input type="text" pattern="[a-z, A-Z]{3,25}" title="Utiliza solo letras" id="nombre" name="nombre" placeholder="Nombre" required class="w-[80%] px-3 py-2 text-gray-500 border-b border-gray-400 bg-transparent shadow-sm">
        
            <label for="email" class="block text-gray-700 text-sm font-bold mb-4"></label>
            <input type="email" id="email" name="email" placeholder="Correo electrónico" required class="w-[80%] px-3 py-2 text-gray-500 border-b border-gray-400 bg-transparent shadow-sm">
        
            <label for="mensaje" class="block text-gray-700 text-sm font-bold mb-4"></label>
            <textarea id="mensaje" name="mensaje" rows="4" placeholder="Mensaje" required class="w-[80%] px-3 py-2 text-gray-500 border-b border-gray-400 bg-transparent shadow-sm"></textarea>
        
            <button type="submit" id="enviar" class="bg-blue-800 hover:bg-blue-950 text-white font-light py-4 px-6 mt-8 rounded-full focus:outline-none focus:shadow-outline">
              Enviar Mensaje
            </button>
          </form>
        </div>
        
      </div>
    </div>
  </Container>
</section>
